Description
Add more information in grid Doorsturen OPV to make it easier to find record.

Solution
Add in Grid Doorsturen OPV the Procesverbaal number this can be found in the Bekeurd persoon/Doorsturen OPV record.
and also add Geimporteerd kolom in the Doorsturen OPV grid. Thyis value indicated if a OPV is imported. This value can be found in the query for OPV in Rapportages.
As seen on screenshot the Geimporteerd J/N values per record.

Test plan
Step 1: Go to generiek - Assistentie open an existing record and add in Rol/proces a Bekeurd persoon
Step 2: This record should be visible in Handhaving -Doorsturen OPV.
Step 3: The Procesverbaal number column should be visible in the grid and also column "Geimporteerd".
Step 4: Proces verbaal number and import status should be according to record.

Navigation
Handhaving - Doorsturen OPV
